metadata.name: Eve #1/2
metadata.description:
At the crossroads.  
Unburdens herself from materialism.  
Ready to carve out her own path.  
Catharsis.

Limited Edition of 10

1st artwork of a series of 7 from the Revival Collection.  
Six 1/1s now listed on Foundation  
https://foundation.app/collection/revivallyonspackphour

A collection of cathartic paintings created to inspire hope for the future.  
Journey of the female psyche.

Curated with theme contributions by packphour.

Oil paintings on paper reinvented with digital paintwork for the screen for our combined visions of the collection.

Oil painting on paper & digital painting.  
3438 x 10170 pix  
350 dpi
